
Info
------------------------------------------------

    Is equivalent to continuous cast statement in switch case
    
Syntax
------------------------------------------------

    case <pattern 1> | <pattern 2> .. => <one or more expressions> #33

Example	
------------------------------------------------
	#33
	scala> val kind = day match {
		case "MON" | "TUE" | "WED" | "THU" | "FRI" =>
		"weekday"
		case "SAT" | "SUN" =>
		"weekend"
	}
